Package: NestedWGCNA
Title: Computation-First Two-Stage Gene Co-Expression Analysis
Version: 1.00
Author: Dai [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Dai <daiki@example.com>
Description: Minimal R implementation of a two-stage gene co-expression
    workflow focused on computation. The package computes adjacency and
    dissimilarity matrices, discovers coarse-grained modules (CGMs), applies
    GenFocus normalization, and discovers fine-grained modules (FGMs).
    No visualization or case-study wrappers are included in this release.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/dai540/NestedWGCNA,
    https://dai540.github.io/NestedWGCNA/
BugReports: https://github.com/dai540/NestedWGCNA/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Suggests:
    dbscan,
    matrixStats,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    uwot
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
